<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
</head>
<body>
    <script>
        let a=6
        let b=5
        if(a<b){
            document.write("Hello,Guna","<br>")
        }else{
            document.write("hi,chandhu","<br>")
        }
        document.write("Brilliant student")

        let name=prompt("Enter your name:") 
        let age=prompt("Enter your age:")
        if(age<18){
            alert(name +" u are too young to marry")
        }else if(age>35){
            alert(name +" u are to old marry")
        }else{
            alert(name +" perfect age to marry")
        }
        alert("welcome to world")
    </script>
</body>
</html>

Conditional Statements:
To make set of instructions(block of code) execute only when the given condition is true.
 Used to decide whether the code has to execute or skip based on the given condition.
Line - line (sequence).
Block of code: set of instructions.
--it will execute only when specific condition is true.
Condition: An expression that evaluates an result(True or False).
Ex: console.log(5>6)
Methods:
if 
If-else
Else if
Switch
Ternary operator 
If: only one possible condition.
--if the condition is true it will execute otherwise it skips.
Syntax:
If(condition){
---block of code
}
Example:
let a=4;
        let b=5;
        if(a<b){
            document.write("Hello,Guna","<br>");
        }
        document.write("Brilliant student")
Output:
Hello,Guna
Brilliant student

If-else:
let a=6
        let b=5
        if(a<b){
            document.write("Hello,Guna","<br>")
        }else{
            document.write("hi,chandhu","<br>")
        }
        document.write("Brilliant student")
Output:
Hi,chandhu
Brilliant student

Else-if:
let name=prompt("Enter your name:") 
        let age=prompt("Enter your age:")
        if(age<18){
            alert(name +" u are too young to marry")
        }else if(age>35){
            alert(name +" u are to old marry")
        }else{
            alert(name +" perfect age to marry")
        }
        alert("welcome to world")
